cast.overview: A woman’s body disappears mysteriously from the morgue without a trace. Police inspector Jaime Peña investigates the strange occurrence with the help of Álex Ulloa, the widower of the missing woman.
cast.title: The Body

cast.original_title: A través de mi ventana 3: A través de tu mirada
cast.overview: After the events of the summer, Ares and Raquel they don't see a way forward in their relationship and decide to go separate ways. But when they meet again in the winter in Barcelona, the love and desire they feel for each other is undeniable. Will they be able to find a way to get back together?
cast.title: Through My Window 3: Looking at You

details.biography:
Oriol Vila Cristóbal (Barcelona, Spain, October 6, 1978) is a Spanish actor. He has been nominated for the Goya Award for Best Newcomer for the film Every Song is About Me (2010).

From Wikipedia (ES), the free encyclopedia
